data.news_body:
Pursuant to Regulation 30 and 33 of the SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015, we hereby inform that the Board of Directors of the Company at their meeting held today i.e. January 18, 2023, have approved the Unaudited Standalone & Consolidated Financial Results as per the Indian Accounting Standards (IND AS) for the quarter and nine months ended December 31, 2022.
